Glow AnyWhere, Anytime! 💫

Wherever you’re headed—weekend getaway, coffee run, or just out the door—our NEW limited-edition AnyWhere Palette is made to Glow with you.
 
Created by Petra and inspired by our London-based bestie @hellokitty, this palette is all about friendship, fun and the everyday joy of Glowing together.
 
Infused with skin-loving ingredients:
❤️ Vitamin E – to nourish
🍏 Apple Seed Oil – rich in Antioxidants
💧 Ceramide NP – for long-lasting hydration
 
Your travel-sized Glow lineup includes:
✨ Cute – soft, pearly highlight
☀️ Subtly Suntouched – natural sun-kissed warmth
🍑 Peachy-y – fresh peachy flush
🌞 Soft – golden bronze Glow
🌹 Rose Dew – fresh rosy radiance
🌅 Summertime – deep bronze lustre
 
Create a fresh, radiant look that’s as joy-inducing as Hello Kitty herself!

Which shade will you Glow for first? Let us know below! 💬
 
#PixiBeauty #PixiGlow #HelloKitty #GlowAnywhere #GlowMeetsBow #SetSailforGlow #TravelWithPixi #OnTheGlow #MakeupWithSkincare #CrueltyFreeBeauty
#AnyWherePalette #PixiFavourites #HelloKittyLovers #SkincareInfusedMakeup

The Brightest Glow Comes from Inside!🌹💚
 
Some of my strongest childhood memories are being with my Grandmother in her café late at night – her still working, everyone sleeping – yet the next day waking up and doing it all over again with a smile and lipstick on!
 
I think she paved the way for me to get up and get on with the day in a positive, Glowing beautiful way.
 
Mother’s Day is SO Important in so many ways, it’s a celebration for all those that have given us wisdom, bedtime stories, unselfish support, endless love and all the things we need to Glow from the inside out!
 
I’m very firm on this belief of mine: we’ve all mothered somebody — a mother to me is someone that nurtures another person selflessly and wants them to have the most Glowing life!
 
xoxo, Petra

Ready to Set the Base for Your Natural Glow? 💚✨
 
The wait is over—the Glow is here! We’ve been listening and we’re beyond thrilled to introduce the newest complexion-perfecting addition to our On-the-Glow family! Meet On-the-Glow Base, the moisturizing, multi-use tinted balm that blurs, brightens and corrects for naturally radiant and even-toned skin-effects. Ceramide NP adds moisture, Superfood Berries gives an antioxidant boost and Fruit Oils smooth and condition for a fresh-faced finish.
 
With 18 flexible shades that lets your natural Glow show, it’s effortless to customize your unique complexion routine:
 
💚 Match your closest tone for an even complexion effect.
💚 Go 1-2 shades lighter to brighten and naturally highlight chosen areas.
💚 Choose 1-2 shades deeper to contour and add a touch of sun-kissed definition.
 
Designed for everyone, this hydrating, sheer and buildable formula delivers an even-toned Glow wherever you go! 
 
Are you ready to Blur, Brighten & Glow? Let us know in the comments! 💚✨
